            <p>Yuji Itadori, a high school student with extraordinary physical abilities, swallows a rotting finger of a powerful Curse named Ryomen Sukuna to save his friends. He soon joins the Tokyo Jujutsu High School to find and consume Sukuna's remaining fingers and eventually execute himself to destroy the Curse forever.</p>
